librarian.feywild.initial:
Hello Stranger, welcome to the Feywild, the wonderful land of fey and magic.
Have you seen a fey yet? They are a bit shy, but with some tasty treats might help you gain their trust.
 Talk to me again if you like to know more about the Fey!
librarian.feywild.borrow: Ah! Curious about the Fey? You can borrow this book, it contains valuable information on the Fey Courts.
librarian.feywild.final: Here to return that book I borrowed you? No worries you can keep it for a while longer. Fair tidings!
librarian.feywild.found: Here to return a book you found? Ah! Curious about the Fey? If you want you can borrow it for a while. Fair tidings!
librarian.feywild.lost: You lost your book? That's ok, you can have another one!
spring_quest_pixie.feywild.summon_messag: Where Am I? Who are you? Are you tasty? Let's go on an adventure! You wanna play? I'm hungry...
spring_quest_pixie.feywild.quest_0_messa: Where Am I? Who are you? Are you tasty? Let's go on an adventure!
spring_quest_pixie.feywild.quest_1_messa: What is that? A Cloud! No Wait, Cotton Candy! It doesn't taste very sweet...
hmm! A sheep you say? Its so fluffy!
It must be lonely thou with out his friend who are all the way in the sky!
What!? It cannot fly? Flying is the best thing there is!
Wish this uhm... meep could experience the joy of flying like his friend can.
Let's make it fly! We must find away!
You're smart ...Or maybe you just have a big head.
Either way I'm sure you will find a way to make this meep fly!
spring_quest_pixie.feywild.quest_2_messa: You made him fly! He must have been so happy!
Wish we had learned it how to land....it's broken now...
spring_quest_pixie.feywild.quest_3_messa: Hey it's you!  You have to taste these red bubbles of sweetness!
Sooo good!‚Äù -The little faerie tries to stuff your face with berries.-
Aaaw now they are all gone...
Maybe I shouldn't have given the last ones to you...
You owe me! Now it's your turn to make me something tasty!
spring_quest_pixie.feywild.quest_4_messa: What is that smell? What are you making?
A cake for me and my feykin?
No, no, no, This treasure is mine! ...uhm ours?
Lets quickly eat it before the other Fey find out!
Phew, I'm stuffed. I think I might die. Huff puff.....got more?
spring_quest_pixie.feywild.quest_5_messa: Oh bravest of gullable wizards, I require your aid!
Just now I was stealing some yummy honey from the Summer Courts Yard.
I got caught by one of the Bee Knights patroling the area and he stole my honey!
and he stole my honey! You have to steal it back for me,
and make those evil Knights pay for their crimes!
You just have to, or...we won't be friends anymore!
spring_quest_pixie.feywild.quest_6_messa: I hope you didn't kill one of those Summer Knights!
Jeez...I said make them pay, like make them give more honey! As payment!
Oh the Honey! Sweet! All Mine now! That will teach those mean Knights.
spring_quest_pixie.feywild.quest_7_messa: Let's plant these saplings, so I will feel more at home!
summer_quest_pixie.feywild.summon_messag: How dare you summon me like I am some sort of magician's Pet. You better know your place....hmph
autumn_quest_pixie.feywild.summon_messag: Darling, what took you so long! I've been waiting for a fine specimen just like you!
winter_quest_pixie.feywild.summon_messag: Such inconvience...why did you summon me Mortal? This ordeal will most certainly lead to your premature demise. But then maybe we can be friends...

message.quest_completion_spring: The spring fey are satisfied with your mischief.
dwarf.feywild.dialogue: <Dwarf> Beardless friend! Talking is cheap, but ores are priceless. So, let's trade!
dwarf.feywild.trade: <Dwarf> Haha, it's always great trading with you!
dwarf.feywild.scroll: <Dwarf> Haha, I like your style. Tell me if you need anything.
message.feywild.dwarf_blacksmith: Use this scroll on a Dwarven Anvil to summon your Dwarven friend.

message.feywild.spring_pixie: A summoning scroll for a Spring Pixie
message.feywild.summer_pixie: A summoning scroll for a Summer Pixie
